    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300015128_7_2312-2384",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "2312-2384",
      "markText": "苏联共产党曾经是国内改革的倡导者，可是过了5年，它却被赶下了政治舞台，而它的一千好几百万党员当中，竟没有一个人站出来捍卫它，这究竟是怎么搞的呢？",
      "totalCount": 532,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300015128&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=2312&rangeEnd=2384",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/35b32f10813ab6c68g018e93?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=2312&rangeEnd=2384"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300015128_4_1876-1900",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "1876-1900",
      "markText": "上帝要惩罚谁，就一定要先把他变成个丧失理智的人。",
      "totalCount": 496,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300015128&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1876&rangeEnd=1900",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/35b32f10813ab6c68g018e93?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1876&rangeEnd=1900"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300015128_9_2603-2652",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "2603-2652",
      "markText": "在推行言论自由的那几年中，人们不是寻找建设性的办法来医治社会疾病，而是利用言论自由来毁灭这个社会。",
      "totalCount": 456,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300015128&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=2603&rangeEnd=2652",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/35b32f10813ab6c68g018e93?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=2603&rangeEnd=2652"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300015128_5_1800-1866",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "1800-1866",
      "markText": "我们要从青少年抓起，要把主要的赌注压在青年身上，要让它变质、发霉、腐烂。我们要把他们变成无耻之徒、庸人和世界主义者。我们一定要做到。",
      "totalCount": 425,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300015128&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1800&rangeEnd=1866",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/35b32f10813ab6c68g018e93?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1800&rangeEnd=1866"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300015128_9_555-605",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "555-605",
      "markText": "联系逐渐变成形式上的和单方面的东西：总是从上到下、从党到群众，很少有自下而上、从群众到党的事情发生。",
      "totalCount": 414,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300015128&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=555&rangeEnd=605",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/35b32f10813ab6c68g018e93?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=555&rangeEnd=605"
    },
    {
